            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is one of the best school here. Good and amazing workplace. The principal of the school is very nice.  She is very co-operative with everyone. Education system is excellent and staff teachers all are so humble and sweet spoken. It focuses on the holistic development of the child. It is fully air-conditioned school. The playground of the school is very big. This school has a good balance between studies and curriculum as well as sports and extracurricular activities.  There is also a special arrangement for karate classes. Highly recommended!!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
