          "reviewBody": "Yadu public school, located in Noida, is a well-regarded institution that is known for its commitment to providing a high-quality education to its students.The school has a dedicated and experienced faculty, and offers a wide range of academic programs that are designed to challenge and inspire students.The school's facilities are modern and well-maintained, providing an ideal learning environment for students.",
          "publisher": {
