            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Kids can learn a lot in this institution. For more than 20 years, it has improved lives and provided education. The school has a distinctive method of instruction that emphasises fun and practical learning, which makes it simpler for pupils to understand. Sports and extracurricular activities are equally valued at schools in addition to academics. Its infrastructure and laboratories meet international standards. The school adopts contemporary teaching techniques and adapts them as necessary. Overall, YPS is an excellent place for kids to learn because it provides all the necessary resources, including teachers, infrastructure, methodologies, and approaches. To all students and parents, I'd suggest YPS.",
